<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.7.3">
<l>karuḷa puṭkoṭi cakka rappaṭai vāṉa nāṭaveṅ kārmukil vaṇṇā</l>
<l>poruḷal lāta veṉṉaip poruḷākki yaṭimai koṇṭāy</l>
<l>teruḷko ṇāṉmaṟai vallavar palarvāḻ cirīvara maṅkalanakarkku</l>
<l>aruḷceytaṅkirun tāyaṟi yēṉoru kaimmāṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O our [lord] with rain cloud colour, you whose land is heaven with the Garuḍa bird banner [and] the discus weapon,</l>
<l>making me who is not a treasure into a treasure you took me into servantship</l>
<l>For you who sit there acting graciously to the city of Cirīvaramaṅkalam where many live</l>
<l>who master the lucid four Vedas I don’t know a substitute.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
